item.title: Thank You Sai
item.description: I am blessed With your love that makes me whole Your love that never takes a toll. No pen can ever explain the divine love, The feeling I am trying to explain Yet all creations cannot seem to stop talking about it. You taught us love You showered us with love, I learned that love, I showed that love. "All things are beautiful seen through the eyes of love" you said, That's when I knew I was beautiful.
